														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4563112">
									

<p>Sometime in 2018, one of my online friends was watching a video of some YouTuber playing a game. I'd never seen it so I asked what it was. He told me it was called &quot;SCP: Secret Lab&quot; and I was like &quot;what's that?&quot; He explained that SCP was its own separate thing and that Secret Lab is just an interpretation of it. He showed me what some of the common SCPs were that he'd reference a lot (like 173, 049, 096, etc.) Honestly, I didn't take a huge interest in it, but randomly two weeks ago, four of the people in our friend group, including me, started getting interested in it again.</p>

							</div>

								
					
