														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4537999">
									

<p>Funny story, actually. I was scrolling through Pinterest, minding my own business when I came across a 'Plague Doctor' picture and saved it to one of my boards. More and more of them started popping up and some of the comments mentioned an 'SCP - 049'. At the time, I had no idea what that was, so it was just a jumble of letters and numbers.</p>
<p>Not long after (about a few hours), I searched it, and found it was a popular site with intresting characters. I ended up being roped into it the more my curiosity grew. SCP - 049 has been, and probably always will be, my favorite SCP. (Kudos to the people who made him!). Now, I'm proud to call myself an SCP Member and am excited to get to work on my own SCP. :D</p>

							</div>

								
					
